1
00:00:38,420 --> 00:00:41,060
=How to Train Your Killer=

2
00:00:41,060 --> 00:00:43,900
=Episode 20=

3
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:50,840
Sit down.

4
00:01:04,040 --> 00:01:04,920
(Father?)

5
00:01:16,070 --> 00:01:17,150
You couldn't catch me.

6
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:29,430
Take a seat.

7
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:43,840
What?

8
00:01:44,950 --> 00:01:45,790
You're tense?

9
00:01:47,070 --> 00:01:47,910
No, I'm not.

10
00:01:53,710 --> 00:01:55,200
Harming her fellow members

11
00:01:55,870 --> 00:01:57,280
always ends like this.

12
00:02:02,790 --> 00:02:04,280
She… she…

13
00:02:04,590 --> 00:02:06,150
Is she gone?

14
00:02:07,350 --> 00:02:08,750
Her life and death

15
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,910
is up to you to decide.

16
00:02:16,470 --> 00:02:19,280
No one can decide

17
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:20,560
another's life or death.

18
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:32,630
All these years,

19
00:02:32,630 --> 00:02:34,630
I've raised you myself.

20
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:37,000
I know your greatest weakness
is your soft heart.

21
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,680
Acting this way

22
00:02:40,870 --> 00:02:42,030
is a grave mistake.

23
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,120
The matter with Bai Jun

24
00:02:44,310 --> 00:02:45,800
was meant as a lesson for you.

25
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,080
I do not know

26
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:53,800
what crime Bai Jun has committed.

27
00:02:54,630 --> 00:02:55,610
His guilt or innocence

28
00:02:55,610 --> 00:02:56,890
is for the authorities to decide.

29
00:02:57,430 --> 00:03:00,190
We only carry out orders.

30
00:03:02,150 --> 00:03:05,360
So some oversights are inevitable.

31
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:07,840
You can't be blamed for this.

32
00:03:08,470 --> 00:03:09,310
But

33
00:03:12,430 --> 00:03:14,000
when mistakes are made,

34
00:03:14,710 --> 00:03:15,750
punishment must follow.

35
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:19,400
You are no exception.

36
00:03:20,350 --> 00:03:24,400
I assigned you
as the Crown Princess's guard,

37
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:26,870
but

38
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:29,000
you seem to be growing closer

39
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:30,430
to Ling Yu.

40
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:32,960
I…

41
00:03:34,310 --> 00:03:36,190
I only did it to hide my true identity.

42
00:03:38,750 --> 00:03:39,590
That's good.

43
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:43,590
I raised you with my own hands.

44
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:48,310
To me, you are as my own child.

45
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:53,240
Never forget where you come from.

46
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:55,960
I understand.

47
00:03:57,870 --> 00:03:58,800
Master,

48
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:01,030
do we have a new mission this time?

49
00:04:04,190 --> 00:04:05,750
Lately, across the martial world,

50
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:08,590
in every stronghold,

51
00:04:08,750 --> 00:04:10,360
spies of unknown origin

52
00:04:11,150 --> 00:04:12,960
have suddenly appeared.

53
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:15,120
I suspect,

54
00:04:16,190 --> 00:04:19,160
the Imperial Court has grown suspicious.

55
00:04:20,870 --> 00:04:23,800
Could it be that the plot to assassinate
the Crown Prince has been exposed?

56
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:26,430
As long as you remain unharmed,

57
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:29,430
our secret will stay hidden.

58
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:33,190
So what you mean is…

59
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:36,190
To keep danger at bay,

60
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:40,870
we must act before they do.

61
00:04:41,950 --> 00:04:45,360
You want me to kill the Crown Prince
right now?

62
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:46,760
No.

63
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,630
I want you to kill...

64
00:05:08,700 --> 00:05:09,580
(Piaoyao Cloth Shop)

65
00:05:12,020 --> 00:05:15,300
(Piaoyao Cloth Shop)

66
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:17,880
Well?

67
00:05:58,190 --> 00:05:59,310
Your favorite candied haws.

68
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:52,430
If I hadn't seen it with my own eyes,

69
00:06:53,510 --> 00:06:54,870
I would never have believed

70
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,390
that the one who planned all of this

71
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:02,390
was actually my biological father.

72
00:07:09,830 --> 00:07:11,240
But there's one thing

73
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:12,950
I just can't figure out.

74
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:16,000
Why would he plot
to kill the Crown Prince?

75
00:07:17,390 --> 00:07:18,430
By doing this,

76
00:07:18,830 --> 00:07:21,430
what benefit could he possibly gain?

77
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:28,120
Now His Majesty lies gravely ill,

78
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:32,160
and the Crown Prince holds full control
of state affairs.

79
00:07:32,550 --> 00:07:34,070
It has long been a foregone conclusion

80
00:07:34,070 --> 00:07:35,880
that he will ascend the throne
in the future.

81
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:38,270
If there's any variable left,

82
00:07:39,310 --> 00:07:41,160
it would be Noble Consort Xiao's son,

83
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:43,070
Second Prince Ling Huan.

84
00:07:43,630 --> 00:07:45,000
But I heard that he's

85
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:47,360
been frail and sickly since childhood.

86
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:50,600
It's precisely because
of his poor health

87
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:55,040
that he could serve well
as a puppet emperor.

88
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:57,950
Prop up the young emperor,

89
00:07:58,510 --> 00:08:00,270
and command the lords in his name.

90
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:04,510
Yet the father I remember
wasn't like that.

91
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:07,360
He was a true pillar of the Court,

92
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,660
always diligent and caring
for the people,

93
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:12,780
treating others with kindness.

94
00:08:13,470 --> 00:08:14,430
Why then would he commit

95
00:08:14,430 --> 00:08:15,820
such a grave act against all order?

96
00:08:18,070 --> 00:08:19,630
This is just his surface.

97
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,800
In my impression,

98
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:26,360
the Master has always been
a cold-blooded and ruthless person

99
00:08:28,190 --> 00:08:30,190
who would stop at nothing
to achieve his goals.

100
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:34,320
Still don't dare to make a move?

101
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:57,390
The law of the jungle

102
00:08:58,910 --> 00:09:01,670
is itself the truth of the world.

103
00:09:04,790 --> 00:09:05,720
Today,

104
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:08,960
you choose mercy toward him,

105
00:09:10,870 --> 00:09:11,710
but tomorrow,

106
00:09:13,030 --> 00:09:15,150
you may fall beneath his blade.

107
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:22,270
I have no fondness for the weak.

108
00:09:23,510 --> 00:09:24,440
Today,

109
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,120
only one of you

110
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:31,840
can leave here.

111
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:55,480
He has always

112
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:58,240
been skilled at playing with hearts.

113
00:09:59,390 --> 00:10:01,080
He's a man of deep schemes.

114
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:04,720
To clear himself of suspicion,

115
00:10:05,500 --> 00:10:06,540
he specifically ordered me

116
00:10:06,550 --> 00:10:08,000
to strike on your wedding night.

117
00:10:09,670 --> 00:10:11,150
Who would have foreseen that?

118
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:14,680
What about this time?

119
00:10:15,690 --> 00:10:16,820
Who does he want me to kill?

120
00:10:27,550 --> 00:10:28,550
This time,

121
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:39,120
he plans to kill his own daughter.

122
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:44,720
I'm asking you
to kill the Crown Princess.

123
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,320
Why?

124
00:10:59,550 --> 00:11:00,480
Why?

125
00:11:04,270 --> 00:11:05,150
I suppose

126
00:11:06,100 --> 00:11:08,190
that if the Crown Prince truly died
by assassination,

127
00:11:09,100 --> 00:11:10,980
and he supported
the young emperor's accession

128
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,510
to become a prime minister,

129
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:15,910
he would ultimately
be a treacherous minister

130
00:11:15,910 --> 00:11:17,240
with an illegitimate claim,

131
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,360
unable to silence public opinion.

132
00:11:26,630 --> 00:11:27,470
But if...

133
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:33,720
But if the one to die were me instead...

134
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:39,080
He could frame the Crown Prince,

135
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:43,910
then march to conquer
with rightful pretext.

136
00:11:46,100 --> 00:11:47,510
Even seizing the throne for himself,

137
00:11:48,790 --> 00:11:50,550
he still seeks a proper pretext.

138
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:53,910
My father...

139
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:57,670
Still cares so much about appearances.

140
00:11:58,750 --> 00:11:59,840
Now it seems

141
00:12:03,790 --> 00:12:05,200
I'm just a pawn

142
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:06,630
on his path to power.

143
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:09,840
When the Master makes up his mind,

144
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:12,480
he never changes it easily.

145
00:12:15,390 --> 00:12:16,600
But this mission…

146
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:19,790
How did you agree to it?

147
00:12:23,870 --> 00:12:25,000
This is not right.

148
00:12:27,320 --> 00:12:28,960
Gu Qingyao is pregnant now.

149
00:12:29,750 --> 00:12:30,590
What?

150
00:12:31,150 --> 00:12:32,150
Is that truly so?

151
00:12:32,750 --> 00:12:33,870
Without a doubt.

152
00:12:34,870 --> 00:12:36,440
Gu Qingyao's pulse indicates joy,

153
00:12:36,800 --> 00:12:38,340
and her face shows signs of pregnancy.

154
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,030
I fear

155
00:12:42,120 --> 00:12:44,030
she's already three months pregnant.

156
00:12:46,670 --> 00:12:47,510
I'm betting

157
00:12:47,510 --> 00:12:49,720
on whether he is truly so heartless,

158
00:12:49,870 --> 00:12:51,720
willing to give up both his own daughter

159
00:12:51,910 --> 00:12:53,480
and the grandchild in her womb.

160
00:12:56,790 --> 00:12:57,720
I've won my bet.

161
00:12:59,080 --> 00:13:01,030
He still has a trace of humanity left.

162
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:03,160
From this day on...

163
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:06,870
From this day on, what should I do?

164
00:13:11,900 --> 00:13:12,840
I've thought it through.

165
00:13:13,870 --> 00:13:14,790
From now on,

166
00:13:14,790 --> 00:13:16,080
no matter what happens,

167
00:13:16,500 --> 00:13:18,550
even if I have to stand
against the entire Pavilion,

168
00:13:18,550 --> 00:13:19,670
and the Master,

169
00:13:21,120 --> 00:13:22,510
I will stay by your side.

170
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:30,840
Your Highness.

171
00:13:31,120 --> 00:13:31,960
Your Highness.

172
00:13:34,960 --> 00:13:36,270
Guard Shi is here as well.

173
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:38,000
It's so late.

174
00:13:38,010 --> 00:13:38,990
Need something from me?

175
00:13:39,750 --> 00:13:41,910
Noble Consort Xiao sent an invitation.

176
00:13:41,910 --> 00:13:43,510
She invites you to offer incense

177
00:13:43,510 --> 00:13:45,150
at the temple tomorrow.

178
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:47,270
Noble Consort Xiao?

179
00:13:47,270 --> 00:13:48,110
Yeah.

180
00:14:01,570 --> 00:14:04,170
♪When a breeze passes by♪

181
00:14:04,690 --> 00:14:08,010
♪The sand and wind burn with longing♪

182
00:14:08,010 --> 00:14:10,650
♪Fearless even when thirst
goes unquenched♪

183
00:14:10,970 --> 00:14:14,130
♪Like a camel wandering
with eyes closed♪

184
00:14:14,490 --> 00:14:17,450
♪When the rain quietly settles♪

185
00:14:17,450 --> 00:14:20,770
♪I think of our sorrow yet unknown♪

186
00:14:20,970 --> 00:14:23,690
♪No need to hum the song of the wind♪

187
00:14:23,850 --> 00:14:27,490
♪Ignoring the sky darkening before us♪

188
00:14:27,650 --> 00:14:29,250
♪I finally understood that truth♪

189
00:14:29,250 --> 00:14:30,730
♪Yet you have already faded away♪

190
00:14:30,930 --> 00:14:32,570
♪I lose my way in the night♪

191
00:14:32,570 --> 00:14:34,050
♪Not knowing how to still my heart♪

192
00:14:34,050 --> 00:14:35,730
♪Loving you feels like lifetimes apart♪

193
00:14:35,730 --> 00:14:38,690
♪Yet longing flows back into verse♪

194
00:14:39,130 --> 00:14:41,570
♪For you and me to meet again♪

195
00:14:42,010 --> 00:14:44,850
♪We must cross a thousand years
of promises♪

196
00:14:45,130 --> 00:14:47,210
♪In the pouring rain♪

197
00:14:47,210 --> 00:14:51,570
♪As if you are still by my side♪
